Name: Parallax Tunnel
About the game: Parallax Tunnel is a first-person flying arcade game. Fly through the tunnel filled with cubes, skillfully dodge them and get points for the distance covered. Over time, the speed of movement through the tunnel will increase and you will have to concentrate so as not to collide with obstacles and not to lose.
